  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this survey of international HIPEC (Hyperthermic Intraperitoneal Chemotherapy)
      surgeons is to determine their knowledge of and attitudes towards the nutritional support
      needs of HIPEC patients and what their practice patterns are with this patient population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
